<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-3">
        <h2>Application uses</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Facilitates Users by one click solution for Medicines & Flu Shots</li>
            <li>Facilitates Pharmacy by providing one stop Solutions</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
        <h2>Features</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Go to SignUp and create your account</li>
            <li>Schedule Appointment or Upload Prescription for Medicines</li>
            <li>Tech Support For Technical Queries & Troubleshooting</li>
            <li>Search Medicines & Book Appointments</li>
            <li>Pharmacies to leverage Digital Solutions</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
        <h2>Overview</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Due to the current pandemic situation all over the world, pharmacy outlets are being frequented by increasingly more people.</li>
           <li>
               Although e-commerce pharmaceutical apps exist, they do not provide customers the ability to reserve medication ahead of time at a particular pharmacy outlet.
            </li>
            <li>
                Similarly, existing applications do not allow users to pre-book flu shot appointments, leading to longer wait times in places where the flu shot is administered.
                “PharmaGo” is an attempt to address these unmet needs.
            </li>
            <li>
                It will provide users with the ability to create an account and register as a new user, reserve a variety of medicines in stock at pharmacy outlets,
                and book appointments for flu shots ahead of time.
            </li>
            <li>This app will contribute to reduced waiting times and increased customer traffic as it helps reduce operational inefficiency. </li>

        </ul>
    </div>
